        "title": "fix(docs): make check:docs work in native PowerShell on Windows",
        "body": "This PR ensures that \\check:docs\\ and doc formatting scripts work correctly when executed in native PowerShell / cmd environments on Windows.\n\nDetails:\n- Add safety checks for child process \\stderr\\ and errors in \\\format-docs.mjs\\ to prevent crashes when spawning oxfmt.\n- Normalize CRLF to LF in \\\format-docs.mjs\\ before comparing raw and formatted file contents.\n- Chunk the list of documents processed by \\oxfmt\\ to bypass command-line length limitations.\n- Ignore \\**/CLAUDE.md\\ in markdownlint checks.\n\nCloses #44293",
